<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Register to Push Messaging</h1>
  </header>

  <main>
    <p>Button should be enabled if your browser supports Service Workers.</p>
    <p>
      <button disabled class="js-push-btn mdl-button mdl-js-button mdl-button--raised mdl-js-ripple-effect">
        Register for Notifications
      </button>
    </p>
    <section class="subscription-details js-subscription-details is-invisible">
      <p>To send push message with data payload click <a id="send-msg" href="/send-msg" data="">Send Push</a>
